
USAGE: startmonitor.sh [OPTIONS]

   Starts a PADRES monitor which can be used to monitor the PADRES broker 
   overlay and its components.
   
OPTIONS:

 JVM Options:
   -Xms, -Xmx            Minimum and Maximum memories for Java virtual machine

 Others:
   -help                 Prints this help
   -b broker_uri         The URI of the broker to connect to. 
                         (optional; default: empty) 

